{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-259-reachable-numbers","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 259: Dostignivi brojevi","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Pozitivan ceo broj naziva se dostižan broj ako može proizaći iz matematičkog izraza koji prati sledeća pravila:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Koriste se cifre od 1 do 9, u tom redosledu i svaka samo jednom puta.</li>\n<li>Bilo koje sledeće cifre mogu se kombinovati (na primer, korišćenjem cifara 2, 3 i 4 dobijamo broj 234).</li>\n<li>Dozvoljeno je korišćenje samo četiri osnovne binarne aritmetičke operacije (sabiranje, oduzimanje, množenje i deljenje).</li>\n<li>Svaka operacija može se koristiti više puta ili ne koristiti uopšte.</li>\n<li>Direktno minus nije prihvaćeno.</li>\n<li>Bilo koji broj običnih zagrada (koje mogu biti ugnježđene) može se koristiti za definisanje redosleda operacija.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Na primer, 42 se može postići, jer $\\frac{1}{23} \\times ((4 \\times 5) - 6) \\times (78 - 9) = 42$.</p>\n<p>Koja je suma svih pozitivnih celih brojeva koji se mogu postići?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4701000cf542c50ff82","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301907,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-259-reachable-numbers"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function reachableNumbers() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nreachableNumbers();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>reachableNumbers()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>20101196798</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(reachableNumbers(), 20101196798);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-201-to-300","dashedName":"problem-259-reachable-numbers","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-260-stone-game","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-258-a-lagged-fibonacci-sequence","id":"5900f4701000cf542c50ff82","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-259-reachable-numbers"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}